Goodbye Solo;;82;;94;;R;;Solo (Souléymane Sy Savané) is a Senegalese cab driver in Winston-Salem, North Carolina, working hard to provide for his wife and child. When he picks up William (Red West), an old man with seemingly nothing left to live for, Solo makes it his personal mission to convince William that life is worth living, despite William's insistence that he just wants to be left alone. As they reveal more of their lives, both men realize they need each other more than either is willing to admit.;;Drama,Comedy;;Ramin Bahrani;;2009;;Souléymane Sy Savané,Red West,Diana Franco Galindo,Lane 'Roc' Williams,Mamadou Lam,Carmen Leyva;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/goodbye_solo